{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be secure and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Secure Financial Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0047AB; /* Deep Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #4682B4; /* Steel Blue */\n            --text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --background-color: #F0F8FF; /* Alice Blue */\n            --footer-background: #003366; /* Darker Blue */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #DDDDDD;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .section p {\n            text-align: justify;\n        }\n\n        .security-features {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 250px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Font Awesome for Icons */\n        .fas, .far {\n            font-family: \"Font Awesome 5 Free\";\n        }\n        .fas.fa-lock, .fas.fa-shield-alt, .fas.fa-key, .fas.fa-file-contract {\n            font-weight: 900;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Secure Financial Consulting</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#security\">Our Commitment</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Your Trusted Partner in Financial Growth</h2>\n            <p>We provide expert financial consulting services tailored to your unique needs. Our mission is to empower you with the insights and strategies required to achieve your financial goals, ensuring security and prosperity every step of the way.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <p>From strategic financial planning and investment management to risk assessment and compliance, we offer a comprehensive suite of services designed to optimize your financial health. We specialize in navigating complex financial landscapes with clarity and precision.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"security\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Commitment to Security</h2>\n            <p>In the world of finance, security is paramount. We employ state-of-the-art security protocols and best practices to safeguard your sensitive financial data. Your privacy and the integrity of your information are our top priorities.</p>\n            <div class=\"security-features\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lock\"></i>\n                    <h3>Data Encryption</h3>\n                    <p>All data is protected with robust encryption methods.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                    <h3>Advanced Threat Protection</h3>\n                    <p>We continuously monitor and defend against potential threats.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-key\"></i>\n                    <h3>Access Control</h3>\n                    <p>Strict access controls ensure only authorized personnel can view your information.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-file-contract\"></i>\n                    <h3>Confidentiality Agreements</h3>\n                    <p>Our team adheres to strict confidentiality policies.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <p>Ready to secure your financial future? Contact us today for a confidential consultation. We are here to guide you towards your financial objectives with unparalleled expertise and unwavering security.</p>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Email: info@securefinancialconsulting.com | Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Secure Financial Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}